{{Infobox book | <!-- See [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Novels]] or [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Books]] --> | name = Fashion, Faith, and Fantasy in the New Physics of the Universe | image = Fashion, Faith, and Fantasy in the New Physics of the Universe.gif | image_size = | border = yes | caption = | author = [[Roger Penrose]] | illustrator = | cover_artist = | country = United States | language = English | series = | subjects = [[Physics]], [[string theory]], [[cosmology]] | publisher = [[Princeton University Press]] | release_date = September 2016 | media_type = Print ([[Hardcover]]), e-book | pages = 512 pp. | isbn = 978-0691119793 | oclc = | congress = | preceded_by = [[Cycles of Time]] | followed_by = }}
'''''Fashion, Faith, and Fantasy in the New Physics of the Universe ''''' is a book by mathematical physicist [[Roger Penrose]], released in September 2016. The book is based on his lectures that he gave at [[Princeton University]] in 2003.<ref>{{cite web|title=MEETING THE KING OF THE TWISTOR|url=http://grahamfarmelo.com/meeting-the-king-of-the-twistor/|publisher=grahamfarmelo.com|accessdate=7 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Fashion, Faith, and Fantasy in the New Physics of the Universe Roger Penrose|url=http://press.princeton.edu/titles/10664.html|website=[[Princeton University Press]]|publisher=press.princeton.edu|accessdate=7 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Roger Penrose: Faith, Fashion and Fantasy in the New Physics of the Universe|url=http://lectures.princeton.edu/2006/roger-penrose/|website=[[Princeton University]]|publisher=lectures.princeton.edu|accessdate=7 June 2016}}</ref>
